unisCBQoSRemarkValue OBJECT-TYPE
    SYNTAX Integer32 (0..4095)
    MAX-ACCESS read-create
    STATUS current
    DESCRIPTION
        "Value to remark:
         for IpPrecedence: 0~7
         for Dscp: 0~63
