unisCBQoSMirrorIfCfgInfoTable OBJECT-TYPE
    SYNTAX SEQUENCE OF UnisCBQoSMirrorIfCfgInfoEntry
    MAX-ACCESS not-accessible
    STATUS current
    DESCRIPTION
