    SYNTAX SEQUENCE OF UnisCBQoSIfClassMatchRunInfoEntry
    MAX-ACCESS not-accessible
    STATUS current
    DESCRIPTION
        "A table of Running statistics for matching a classifier
         in a QoS policy applied on the interface."
